imdb.plot outline: There is an unfixable problem in the almighty BANK of all BANKS that cannot be fixed by the status quo of money printing. The consequences are about to become dire, yet very few can foresee the ramifications. An underground revolution has begun to wake up those capable of reacting in time, and enlightening their financial education to endure the challenges ahead. The fiat wars are sinking to and end, but on the other end is hope. Crypto and Metals now fight on behalf of the people who own them to appreciate in value as the years go on. This is the greatest battle of our time.
